msgstr "Accurate: one ffmpeg call per thumbnail, seek after input (slow, frame-accurate). Fast: seek before input per thumbnail for wide intervals, or one fps decode pass per tile for intervals of 5s or less. Experimental: one file open with seek between captures (PyAV when available, otherwise one ffmpeg process with many seeks per tile)."

